content: I paid for this app to install it on my tablet but if I want to install it on the phone I need to pay for it again?
replyContent: Thanks for your feedback. You can use apps you bought on Google Play on any Android device without paying again. However, each device must have the same Google Account on it. Please, read more here: https://bit.ly/2EJCYvP . If you have troubles or questions, please contact our support and we will help.
